      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that kind of thing. i don't want to talk to a stranger on a helpline or some friend who's just gonna give me the same \"it'll get better\" speech. they don't get it. it's not just being sad, it's like the physical reality of everything is just... gone. i feel like i'm just a hollow shell of a person. everything feels so heavy and pointless. what's even the point of talking about it when it's not going to change the fact that my entire life is over?",
